OL,3,CRoad remains closed after burst water
OL,4,Cpipe causes sinkhole
OL,6,FA gaping hole was visible on a
OL,7,FLeicester road after workers had to
OL,8,Ffix a burst water pipe and sinkhole.
OL,10,FThe sinkhole appeared on Monday
OL,11,Fmorning (29 December) as water was
OL,12,Fseen gushing from a pipe in Victoria
OL,13,FRoad East, at the crossroads with
OL,14,FGipsy Lane, in Humberstone.
OL,16,FEmergency services were at the scene
OL,17,Ffor more than 24 hours as repairs took
OL,18,Fplace.
