OL,6,FWorkers appear to have had to dig up a
OL,7,Flarger portion of the road, but Severn
OL,8,FTrent said the pipe has now been fixed.
OL,10,FThe crossroads remained closed on
OL,11,FWednesday, as disruption continued for
OL,12,Fresidents and nearby businesses.
OL,14,FA Severn Trent spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"We're continuing to make repairs on
OL,16,FVictoria Road East following a burst
OL,17,Fwater pipe.
