OL,6,F"While the pipe has now been fixed,
OL,7,Fthe complexity of the road repair
OL,8,Fmeans we won't be able to reopen the
OL,9,Froad fully until at least next week.
OL,11,F"We appreciate the disruption this
OL,12,Fwill cause and thank everyone for
OL,13,Ftheir patience while we work as
OL,14,Fquickly as we can.
